Definition: a family of languages of the Fulani of West Africa and used as a lingua franca in the sub-Saharan regions from Senegal to Chad
Example: the best known of the West African languages
Synonyms: Ful, Fulani, Peul, West_African, a, family, of, languages, the, West, Africa, and, used, as, lingua, franca, in, sub-Saharan, regions, from, Senegal, to, Chad, best, known, African
Category: noun.communication
